graph TB
    subgraph "ModelMesh Serving Component"
        Controller[modelmesh-controller<br/>Deployment]
        Webhook[Validation Webhook<br/>9443/TCP HTTPS]
        MetricsService[Metrics Service<br/>8443/TCP HTTPS]

        Controller -->|validates via| Webhook
        Controller -->|exposes| MetricsService
    end

    subgraph "Runtime Pods (per ServingRuntime)"
        direction TB
        ModelMesh[ModelMesh Container<br/>gRPC routing layer]
        RuntimeAdapter[Runtime Adapter<br/>Protocol translator]
        ModelServer[Model Server<br/>Triton/MLServer/OVMS/TorchServe]
        RESTProxy[REST Proxy<br/>8008/TCP optional]
        StorageHelper[Storage Helper<br/>Init/Sidecar]

        RESTProxy -->|translates to gRPC| ModelMesh
        ModelMesh -->|routes to| RuntimeAdapter
        RuntimeAdapter -->|manages| ModelServer
        StorageHelper -->|loads models for| ModelServer
    end

    subgraph "Custom Resources"
        InferenceServiceCR[InferenceService CR<br/>serving.kserve.io/v1beta1]
        PredictorCR[Predictor CR<br/>serving.kserve.io/v1alpha1]
        ServingRuntimeCR[ServingRuntime CR<br/>serving.kserve.io/v1alpha1]
        ClusterServingRuntimeCR[ClusterServingRuntime CR<br/>serving.kserve.io/v1alpha1]
    end

    User[User/System] -->|creates| PredictorCR
    User -->|creates| ServingRuntimeCR
    User -->|creates| InferenceServiceCR
    Admin[Admin] -->|creates| ClusterServingRuntimeCR

    PredictorCR -->|watched by| Controller
    ServingRuntimeCR -->|watched by| Controller
    InferenceServiceCR -->|watched by| Controller
    ClusterServingRuntimeCR -->|watched by| Controller

    Controller -->|creates| RuntimeDeployment[Runtime Deployment]
    Controller -->|creates| K8sService[Kubernetes Service<br/>8033 gRPC, 8008 REST]
    RuntimeDeployment -->|contains| ModelMesh

    subgraph "External Dependencies"
        etcd[etcd<br/>2379/TCP<br/>Model metadata & routing]
        S3[Object Storage<br/>S3/MinIO<br/>443/TCP HTTPS]
        K8sAPI[Kubernetes API<br/>6443/TCP HTTPS]
        Prometheus[Prometheus<br/>Metrics collection]
    end

    Controller -->|watches/manages| K8sAPI
    ModelMesh -->|stores metadata| etcd
    StorageHelper -->|pulls models| S3
    MetricsService -->|scraped by| Prometheus
    ModelMesh -->|exposes metrics to| Prometheus

    subgraph "Internal ODH Integration"
        ServiceMesh[Service Mesh - Istio<br/>Optional mTLS]
        ModelRegistry[Model Registry<br/>Model metadata]
        MonitoringStack[Monitoring Stack<br/>Prometheus Operator]
    end

    K8sService -.->|optional| ServiceMesh
    StorageHelper -.->|may reference| ModelRegistry
    MetricsService -->|ServiceMonitor| MonitoringStack

    Client[Inference Client] -->|gRPC 8033 or HTTP 8008| K8sService
    K8sService -->|routes to| ModelMesh

